Disconnect by closing the FD outside of the PortalManager causes select to throw errors.  Fix is to pass a PortalManager pointer to each Portal object. This allows Portal to call PortalManager::disconnect and pass itself in.  PortalManager can then do all the voodoo that it needs to do.
